  "prompt": "How do I contact Handy customer service?",
  "response": "To contact Handy customer service, you have several options:\n\n1. **Email**: You can reach out to Handy's customer support team by sending an email to support@handy.com. They typically respond within 24-48 hours.\n\n2. **Phone**: Handy's customer service phone number is 1-844-426-3946. They are available Monday through Friday from 9 AM to 5 PM EST.\n\n3. **In-app support**: If you have the Handy app installed on your mobile device, you can access customer support directly through the app. Simply navigate to the \"Help\" or \"Support\" section, and you'll be able to submit a request or find answers to common questions.\n\n4. **Social media**: You can also reach out to Handy through their social media channels, such as Twitter (@Handy) or Facebook (facebook.com/Handy). They typically respond to messages and comments within a reasonable timeframe.\n\nWhen contacting Handy customer service, be sure to have your account information and any relevant details about your issue or question ready, so they can assist you more efficiently.",
